\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/la-neem-trong-sorion-300x300.jpg 300w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/la-neem-trong-sorion-261x261.jpg 261w\" alt=\"la-neem-thanh-phan-chinh-sorion\" width=\"338\" height=\"338\" \/><\/div>\n<div id=\"toc_container\" class=\"toc_light_blue no_bullets\"><p class=\"toc_title\">N\u1ed9i dung ch&iacute;nh<\/p><ul class=\"toc_list\"><li><a href=\"#Neem_Azadirachta_Indica\"><span class=\"toc_number toc_depth_1\">1<\/span> Neem (Azadirachta Indica)<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#Sweet_Indrajao_Wrightia_Tinctoria\"><span class=\"toc_number toc_depth_1\">2<\/span> Sweet Indrajao (Wrightia Tinctoria)<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#Goc_nhuom_Rubia_cordifolia\"><span class=\"toc_number toc_depth_1\">3<\/span> G\u1ed1c nhu\u1ed9m (Rubia cordifolia)<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#Dau_dua_Cocos_nucifera\"><span class=\"toc_number toc_depth_1\">4<\/span> D\u1ea7u d\u1eeba (Cocos nucifera)<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#Bo_hat_mo_Butyrospermum_Parkii\"><span class=\"toc_number toc_depth_1\">5<\/span> B\u01a1 h\u1ea1t m\u1ee1 (Butyrospermum Parkii)<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#Cu_nghe_Curcuma_Longa\"><span class=\"toc_number toc_depth_1\">6<\/span> C\u1ee7 ngh\u1ec7 (Curcuma Longa)<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/div>\n<h4 class=\"vc_custom_heading\"><span id=\"Neem_Azadirachta_Indica\">Neem (Azadirachta Indica)<\/span><\/h4>\n<div id=\"tb-5f85cd33cf755\" class=\"li-textblock         \">\n<p>C\u00e2y neem \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i c\u00e2y c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong ch\u1eefa b\u1ec7nh, l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m ng\u1ee9a v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam m\u1ea1nh. Hoa, l\u00e1, qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 r\u1ec5 c\u1ee7a c\u00e2y\u00a0c\u00f3 v\u00e0i tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong\u00a0y h\u1ecdc Ayurvedic. D\u1ea7u neem thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c h\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a c\u00e2y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn do t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ng n\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong Ayurveda cho \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ec7nh v\u1ec1 da v\u00e0 vi\u00eam kh\u1edbp. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, d\u1ea7u neem c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"vc_column-inner \">\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n<div id=\"img-5f85cd33cfaf7\" class=\"li-image  center        \"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/xuyen-thao-trong-sorion.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 338px) 100vw, 338px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/xuyen-thao-trong-sorion.jpg 338w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/xuyen-thao-trong-sorion-150x150.jpg 150w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/xuyen-thao-trong-sorion-300x300.jpg 300w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/xuyen-thao-trong-sorion-261x261.jpg 261w\" alt=\"xuyen-thao-trong-sorion\" width=\"338\" height=\"337\" \/><\/div>\n<h4 class=\"vc_custom_heading\"><span id=\"Sweet_Indrajao_Wrightia_Tinctoria\">Sweet Indrajao (Wrightia Tinctoria)<\/span><\/h4>\n<div id=\"tb-5f85cd33d0153\" class=\"li-textblock         \">\n<p>\u1ede \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e2y hoa c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb x\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn nay. \u1ede d\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 b\u1ed9t, v\u1ecf c\u00e2y, h\u1ea1t, l\u00e1 v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 r\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c nhau cho m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch y h\u1ecdc \u2013 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb \u0111au d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y, b\u1ec7nh v\u1ea9y n\u1ebfn v\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 da li\u1ec5u kh\u00e1c. Sweet Indrajao (Wrightia Tinctoria) c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng g\u00e0u; do \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong c\u00e1c ch\u1ebf ph\u1ea9m d\u1ea7u t\u00f3c.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"vc_column-inner \">\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n<div id=\"img-5f85cd33d06a8\" class=\"li-image  center        \"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Faerberwurzel-thanh-phan-sorion.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 338px) 100vw, 338px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Faerberwurzel-thanh-phan-sorion.jpg 338w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Faerberwurzel-thanh-phan-sorion-150x150.jpg 150w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Faerberwurzel-thanh-phan-sorion-300x298.jpg 300w\" alt=\"Faerberwurzel-thanh-phan-sorion\" width=\"338\" height=\"336\" \/><\/div>\n<h4 class=\"vc_custom_heading\"><span id=\"Goc_nhuom_Rubia_cordifolia\">G\u1ed1c nhu\u1ed9m (Rubia cordifolia)<\/span><\/h4>\n<div id=\"tb-5f85cd33d0ccd\" class=\"li-textblock         \">\n<p>G\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e2y thu\u1ed1c nhu\u1ed9m, c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Manjistha. T\u1ea1i \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e2y \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh v\u1ec1 da quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ayurveda. B\u1ed9t m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1eeb r\u1ec5 kh\u00f4 c\u1ee7a c\u00e2y n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong y h\u1ecdc Ayurvedic, trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p nh\u01b0 v\u1ea9y n\u1ebfn, eczema, ng\u1ee9a, vi\u00eam da c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ecba, b\u1ecfng v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed\u00a0l\u00e0 c\u00e1c\u00a0kh\u1ed1i u l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh hay \u00e1c t\u00ednh. Ch\u00fang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9, t\u1eeb c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng n\u00f3ng \u1edf ph\u00eda nam \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng \u00f4n \u0111\u1edbi \u1edf ch\u00e2n d\u00e3y Himalaya. N\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t\u00a0c\u00f3 c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t\u00a0l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng pH.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"vc_column-inner \">\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n<div id=\"img-5f85cd33d1058\" class=\"li-image  center        \"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/dau-dua-sorion.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 338px) 100vw, 338px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/dau-dua-sorion.jpg 338w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/dau-dua-sorion-150x150.jpg 150w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/dau-dua-sorion-300x300.jpg 300w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/dau-dua-sorion-261x261.jpg 261w\" alt=\"dau-dua-sorion\" width=\"338\" height=\"338\" \/><\/div>\n<h4 class=\"vc_custom_heading\"><span id=\"Dau_dua_Cocos_nucifera\">D\u1ea7u d\u1eeba (Cocos nucifera)<\/span><\/h4>\n<div id=\"tb-5f85cd33d18f7\" class=\"li-textblock         \">\n<p>D\u1ea7u d\u1eeba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi trong ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da v\u00e0 t\u00f3c, ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u\u00a0axit amin\u00a0v\u00e0 vitamin.\u00a0Ngo\u00e0i ra, n\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a\u00a0nhi\u1ec1u\u00a0axit b\u00e9o nh\u01b0 axit lauric v\u00e0 caprylic, ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1ng sinh t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfi virus, vi khu\u1ea9n, n\u1ea5m, k\u00fd sinh tr\u00f9ng v\u00e0 vi tr\u00f9ng. C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i d\u1ea7u th\u01a1m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m, \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng acid-base c\u1ee7a da v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da. \u1ede \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9, d\u1ea7u d\u1eeba c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u00a0cho c\u00e1c v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng\u00a0do t\u00ednh kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n, kh\u00e1ng virus v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ng n\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi n\u00f3 l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m ng\u1ee9a v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 da trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u1eefa b\u1ec7nh t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a n\u00f3.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"vc_column-inner \">\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n<div id=\"img-5f85cd33d2507\" class=\"li-image  center        \"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/bo-hat-mo-sorion.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 338px) 100vw, 338px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/bo-hat-mo-sorion.jpg 338w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/bo-hat-mo-sorion-150x150.jpg 150w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/bo-hat-mo-sorion-300x300.jpg 300w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/bo-hat-mo-sorion-261x261.jpg 261w\" alt=\"bo-hat-mo-thanh-phan-sorion\" width=\"338\" height=\"338\" \/><\/div>\n<h4 class=\"vc_custom_heading\"><span id=\"Bo_hat_mo_Butyrospermum_Parkii\">B\u01a1 h\u1ea1t m\u1ee1 (Butyrospermum Parkii)<\/span><\/h4>\n<div id=\"tb-5f85cd33d3039\" class=\"li-textblock         \">\n<p>B\u01a1 h\u1ea1t m\u1ee1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da linh ho\u1ea1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cung c\u1ea5p. N\u00f3 c\u1ef1c\u00a0ch\u1ee9a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho\u00a0da nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c vitamin, kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u00e1c axit b\u00e9o kh\u00f4ng b\u00e3o h\u00f2a. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao vitamin E, provitamin A, k\u1ebdm, allantoin v\u00e0 axit b\u00e9o omega-3, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 da trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o, gi\u00fap x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 l\u00e0m cho da kh\u00f4 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i v\u00e0\u00a0m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i\u00a0tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. B\u01a1 h\u1ea1t m\u1ee1 c\u0169ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ebf b\u00e0o t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y ch\u1eefa l\u00e0nh c\u00e1c v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u1ebft s\u1eb9o v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o cao nh\u01b0ng b\u01a1 h\u1ea1t m\u1ee1 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i\u00a0nh\u1eddn\u00a0tr\u00ean da.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"vc_column-inner \">\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n<div id=\"img-5f85cd33d37ac\" class=\"li-image  center        \"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/nghe-trong-sorion.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 338px) 100vw, 338px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/nghe-trong-sorion.jpg 338w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/nghe-trong-sorion-150x150.jpg 150w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/nghe-trong-sorion-300x300.jpg 300w, http:\/\/sorion.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/nghe-trong-sorion-261x261.jpg 261w\" alt=\"nghe-trong-sorion\" width=\"338\" height=\"338\" \/><\/div>\n<h4 class=\"vc_custom_heading\"><span id=\"Cu_nghe_Curcuma_Longa\">C\u1ee7 ngh\u1ec7 (Curcuma Longa)<\/span><\/h4>\n<div id=\"tb-5f85cd33d3e44\" class=\"li-textblock         \">\n<p>C\u1ee7 ngh\u1ec7, c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 ngh\u1ec7, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e2y thu\u1ed1c Ayurvedic quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. \u1ede \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9, vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh trong \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4000 n\u0103m. N\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i da \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh v\u1ec1 da nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 b\u1ec7nh v\u1ea9y n\u1ebfn. Curcumin ch\u1ee9a trong c\u1ee7 ngh\u1ec7 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam, ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i vi khu\u1ea9n, virus v\u00e0 k\u00fd sinh tr\u00f9ng. N\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng, \u0111au v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ung th\u01b0, v\u00ec ch\u1ea5t curcumin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1ebf b\u00e0o b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng, k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u1ea1n \u0111ang th\u1eafc m\u1eafc\u00a0th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Sorion\u00a0l\u00e0 g\u00ec? N\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t, th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean? B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p cho b\u1ea1n. Sorion v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a h\u01a1n 70 lo\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u1ec7u, c\u00e2y thu\u1ed1c qu\u00fd \u1edf \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi t\u1eeb y h\u1ecdc Ayurvedic. Trong \u0111\u00f3&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":139,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[17],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/sorizon.ninhbinhsite.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/137"}],"collection"